                    Compare Reviews for Annuities
                
            Annuities are often touted as an investment, but they actually work more like an insurance policy. When you buy an annuity, you pay a company a set amount of money and are guaranteed to get a lump sum of cash every month for the rest of your life.The complicated part is figuring out whether or not buying an annuity makes sense for you. There are a lot of extra costs with an annuity versus a traditional investment portfolio, but you may be eligible for tax benefits.
                            Read more
                        
                        
